  "keyFeatures": [
    "Custom schema builder with Likert, boolean, free-text, and multi-select field types",
    "Dynamic annotation form renderer driven by JSON schema definitions at runtime",
    "Sequential annotation flow with auto-advance and per-project progress tracking",
    "Round-robin task assignment via stored procedure distributing items across annotators",
    "Inter-annotator agreement scoring computed per field using stored procedures",
    "AI flagging pipeline powered by Claude API to detect and explain annotator divergence",
    "JSON export of flattened annotations with AI flags for ML training pipelines",
    "One-command Docker Compose deployment with MySQL, FastAPI, and Next.js"
  ],
